  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Safe water springs for 3118 people in Ruteete</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project will construct 6 protected water springs in 3 villages of Kyamusa Kyairweisenya and Kimuhon which will serve over 3118 people who are in dire need of safe  (hygienically clean), and reliable water as per our field visits. The provision of protected springs will significantly reduce water borne diseases and will improve the health of women and girls. Children&apos;s performance in schools will increase as they will easily fetch water and women will have time for more profitable activities.</narrative>
  </description>
